                        <p>Pike hopes to continue the trend of widening the scope of S4S B4B.</p>
<p>“We need to grow beyond our own realm,” Eckberg said. “This event is not so much about Pike as it is about cancer patients worldwide and Duke coming together as a whole. If we really want to raise more money and get more people involved, we need to expand past the Duke community and far beyond it.”</p>

